1
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,320
Why?

2
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,750
Why take everyone around me

3
00:00:44,750 --> 00:00:45,350
away?

4
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:49,430
Why has my whole life been

5
00:00:49,470 --> 00:00:51,320
an unmarked grave for others?

6
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:52,920
Why?

7
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:54,790
Miss He,

8
00:00:55,790 --> 00:00:56,960
you need not be hostile to me.

9
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,390
Every life has its own place

10
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:00,880
and its own bounds.

11
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,150
Duan Xu

12
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:04,680
paid with his life

13
00:01:05,310 --> 00:01:06,430
to give you the five senses.

14
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:08,950
It was to uphold order.

15
00:01:13,070 --> 00:01:13,680
Order?

16
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:29,870
I was born without the five senses.

17
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,840
This is order.

18
00:01:34,310 --> 00:01:36,200
I was forced onto the throne
of the Sovereign of Spirits.

19
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:37,790
This is order too.

20
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:40,430
Immortal.

21
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:42,920
I am not a tool

22
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,790
for you to uphold the world's order.

23
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,920
Duan Xu

24
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,950
shouldn't be

25
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,640
your sacrifice to keep order!

26
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,350
I can save him.

27
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:20,710
Why help me?

28
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,190
It's not help.

29
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,310
It's a reward

30
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:27,120
for your devotion to

31
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:28,190
balancing the Mortal and Spirit Worlds.

32
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:29,840
And he,

33
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,150
with his fragile mortal body

34
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:33,280
and will to live,

35
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:34,470
defied fate,

36
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:36,750
love hate, joy, sorrow;

37
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,240
birth, aging, sickness, death.

38
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,910
That deserves respect.

39
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,930
In the name of Lord of Fate,

40
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,190
I grant you both new destinies.

41
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:48,840
Take good care

42
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:50,630
of yourselves.

43
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:18,870
Duan Xu.

44
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,590
Duan Xu.

45
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:26,450
笙ｪFalling down like snow笙ｪ

46
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:30,400
笙ｪJoys and sorrows of the mortal world笙ｪ

47
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:34,280
笙ｪSwept along by the daylight笙ｪ

48
00:04:34,690 --> 00:04:38,490
笙ｪThe forms and hues of the mortal realm笙ｪ

49
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:41,430
笙ｪLingering for a fleeting moment笙ｪ

50
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:45,910
笙ｪWas once touched by laughing tears笙ｪ

51
00:04:46,390 --> 00:04:49,300
笙ｪIf I could live a simple life笙ｪ

52
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,140
笙ｪFor once笙ｪ

53
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:53,480
笙ｪI'd be a guest in a sweet dream笙ｪ

54
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:53,950
Simu.

55
00:04:57,310 --> 00:05:00,810
笙ｪDawn and dusk rise and set笙ｪ

56
00:05:00,990 --> 00:05:04,610
笙ｪLonging to meet, yet parted by destiny笙ｪ

57
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:08,730
笙ｪLet me wander through笙ｪ

58
00:05:08,730 --> 00:05:12,370
笙ｪLight and dark,ﾂwithout turning back笙ｪ

59
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:16,180
笙ｪWander to the other shore
with the lantern笙ｪ

60
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:20,310
笙ｪAccompanied by eternity笙ｪ

61
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:22,280
笙ｪAs all things turn and flow笙ｪ

62
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,120
I can save him.

63
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,950
But you'll lose your spirit power.

64
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:28,480
And become a mortal.

65
00:05:31,430 --> 00:05:32,070
Are you willing to

66
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,510
pay this price?

67
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,360
Being mortal is my lifelong wish.

68
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,120
How could that be called a price?

69
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:47,090
笙ｪA lone lamp shines on the other shore笙ｪ

70
00:05:47,090 --> 00:05:51,060
笙ｪAccompanied by the abyss笙ｪ

71
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:53,910
笙ｪMoments may last笙ｪ

72
00:05:54,140 --> 00:06:04,010
笙ｪLove and hate will fade away笙ｪ
